commitResults.messageTitle: Modify edit command to account for access rights
commitResults.messageBody:
EditCommand is generalised for all users which allows unauthorised
users to edit other users' details and restricted fields.

Modifying the edit command to account for access rights will
resolve this and ensure that only authorised edit command calls
are allowed.

Lets,
* change EditCommand to an abstract class and create child classes
EditOthersCommand and EditSelfCommand to account for different
edit command syntax
* modify EditCommandParser to return the right type of EditCommand
and conduct checks to ensure access rights for respective edit
command calls
